{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act19side", "eventName": "綠野幻夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DV-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "多蘿西的承諾", "storyInfo": "原來進入實驗室才是拓荒者們的真正目的，他們認為多蘿西是神秘生物失控的始作俑者，而在他們發動攻擊之時，這種神秘的生物卻彷彿具備了自我意識，主動保護多蘿西。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g8_alley_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......繆爾賽思。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......嗯......", "name": "繆爾賽思"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有料到你在這裡。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#7$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#7$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱......歉？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是博士提醒，我差一點親手殺死你。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是敵人想看見的嗎？他們想讓你變成殺害前同僚的兇手？", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未必。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能及時收手，除了博士出聲提醒，還有她那句話的緣故。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不要急著與任何人為敵”——她有意預告了繆爾賽思的出現。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這解釋了她之前的行為疑點。;她想引導我們找到繆爾賽思。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line32", "option2": "line32"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難不成她故意把繆爾賽思送了回來？", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可剛才的情況明明很兇險，誰能保證繆爾賽思不會死在我們手上......", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了，她不在乎繆爾賽思到底是死是活。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這對她來說是一場測試。;她想讓塞雷婭加快行動。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line41", "option2": "line46"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line49"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......測試動力甲的技術，也測試我和羅德島的反應。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在酒吧裡說的每一句話都是對我的試探。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#3$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line49"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她仍在引導我們走向對她有利的方向。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃呃呃......！", "name": "繆爾賽思"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繆爾賽思，你好些了嗎？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#5$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在好幾個小時前給你注射了鎮定劑，你在動力甲裡面的時候已經基本恢復了清醒。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當前體驗到的暈眩與麻痺，主要是缺氧和精神恐懼帶來的後遺症。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經為你做了一些應急處理，但完全恢復還需要半個小時左右。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阻......阻......", "name": "繆爾賽思"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阻止？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阻止......誰？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想讓我們阻止那個把你關進動力甲裡的人嗎？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那位黎博利嗎？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......", "name": "繆爾賽思"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為著急，繆爾賽思的額頭和手背上冒出了細密的汗珠。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 40.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然抓住了你的手，伴隨著她的動作，水滴紛紛浮了起來，狠狠撞上你的衣襟。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "水在深色的布料上迅速洇開，組成了一行訊息。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是那個黎博利的名字，不是斐爾迪南，而是......"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......359。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "359號基地。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g9_headquarter", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很少來這裡。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好歹你送了我一張臨時工牌。", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“文獻學顧問”——萊茵這種科技公司，真的需要這方面的顧問嗎？", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的心情很好，這是否說明，實驗進展還不錯？", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別提實驗。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十分鐘。像我這樣的人，一天下來，只有十分鐘是我自己的。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以把這時間花在跟孩子們打視訊電話上，也可以用這短暫的時間和埃琳娜他們一起吃個晚飯。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我更喜歡什麼都不做，就站在這裡看看這一切。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外面只有街道。", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這就是一切。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g7_mainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_523_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 10.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 400.0, "fadetime": 10.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像這樣工作一整天，他們必定滿身疲憊。為什麼他們的臉上看不見沮喪，腳步也依然輕快？", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為“機會”。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們相信自己的辛勞將有機會帶給全家人更好的生活。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......就跟城外那些拓荒者一樣。", "name": "霍爾海雅"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，就像拓荒者。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特里蒙，三馱鎮。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經只有三匹馱獸帶著七個拓荒者，在這片土地上建起了第一個簡陋的定居點。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今呢？看看我們腳下的街道。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡聚集了最有活力的開拓者和開拓者們的後代。沒有哪個國家富有哥倫比亞的進取精神。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥倫比亞的繁榮給了人們信心，而人們日復一日地不斷前進也會給哥倫比亞帶來生機。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要哥倫比亞保持飛速前進，那這片土地上每一個人的生活也都在前進。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g9_headquarter", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你們是怎麼看我的。你，克麗斯騰，塞雷婭......你們都叫我“投機者”。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能抓住機會的，可都是聰明人。", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不否認，我喜歡站在這裡，這個更高的位置，而不是下面。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我配得上我得到的機會。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的項目帶來財富，財富推動下一個項目，技術因此而不斷進步——", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們將站在其他所有國家前面，引領整個泰拉進入新的時代。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那個時候，後人會豎起不朽的豐碑，上面將刻有我們的名字。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們？", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勝利屬於每一個開拓者。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十分鐘快到了。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可沒給我說話的時間。", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霍爾海雅，我知道你來找我是要說什麼。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原諒你。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "霍爾海雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_536_1#3$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰，繆爾賽思，塞雷婭，帕爾維斯......還有你。我沒有時間浪費在猜測你們各自的小心思上。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西的實驗距離成功只有一步之遙——", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只想要那個最後的結果。", "name": "斐爾迪南"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_522_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑、桑尼......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西說過了，這裡沒有危險......你們為什麼都掏出了弓弩？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有危險？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏比卡博士，你錯了。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們面前的就是最大的危險。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是指......多蘿西？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你願意聽我們解釋......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩你和兩位醫生讓一讓。我們的目標從來都不是你們。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，我們上了這位領隊先生的當。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才那場被阻止的針對喬伊絲的襲擊，只是一場刻意的表演。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他先後讓我們看到了他的憤怒、他的猶豫和他的底線，只為了掩蓋一件事——", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從始至終，他都做好了真正去犯罪的準備。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有料到邁爾會動手。為了取得你們......尤其是烏比卡博士的信任，我原本安排了薩姆來扮演更激進的一方。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，這些都不重要。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經如願來到了這裡，找到了問題的源頭——", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，你策劃那場綁架，又一路來到這裡，是想殺了我嗎？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能不能問一問......為什麼？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依舊是溫柔到能滲進最堅硬的心臟裡的聲音。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那雙濕潤的、微微睜大的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼無辜，那麼驚訝，甚至帶著一絲受傷。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像該被指責的是被迫拿起武器自衛的他們一樣。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼......你問我為什麼？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我都看見了。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你造出來的怪物一路追殺我們，你用我的同伴們的鮮血餵養這些怪物......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這個......邪惡的......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並不存在什麼怪物！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些只是實驗的副產物，由一種對神經信號敏感的特殊物質構成......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，埃琳娜，這不是桑尼的臆測。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#3$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的意思恐怕是，他的確早就見過那些銀色物體......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至更多。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#4$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是的。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三天前，我偷偷溜進了實驗區......我想來找你。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想......呃，那時候我想來問問你，我能不能報名成為受試者。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領隊，你不是說，成為受試者有很大風險，這些大公司很可能在騙我們嗎？", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風險......哈......哈哈哈！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起。薩姆，我是個言行不一致的混蛋......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#9$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我想糾正我曾經的錯誤。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#9$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽著，各位——", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一夜，我看到銀色的怪物在她身邊凝聚成形，她對它們說話，就好像那是她的寵物一樣。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西·弗蘭克斯就是這場災難的始作俑者。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g3_cottage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪麗女士，我說的這些，您是不是很難接受？", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不是喜歡看科幻電影的那類人。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那或許您可以看一眼這封信。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信？", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼先生跟我巡完線之後，可能料到了之後會有危險，把這封信交給了我。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說——“萬一我出事了，請把這封信交給瑪麗·班納”。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他應該不介意......您提前看到信的內容吧？", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......給我吧。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，信上......說了什麼？", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那傢伙到底去了哪裡？！", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#5$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格雷伊，你並不瞭解桑尼·羅馬諾。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的內心充滿了憤恨。因為那份該死的保險......", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是保險......", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#5$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，在哥倫比亞，這是個刻在所有感染者腦子裡的詞語。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許......很多外頭的人會覺得哥倫比亞對感染者已經足夠仁慈。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“只要能支付醫療保險費用，就可以獲得後續正常生活的保障”——聽起來是不是還挺公正的？", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼在剛得病的時候也是這麼對我說的。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是結果呢？", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是不是一筆......非常巨額的費用？", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道就算我當一輩子警察，不吃不喝都負擔不起。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那玩意兒就不是用來保障感染者生活的......巨額保費與他們能得到的藥品完全不匹配。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是一筆罰款，一條隱藏的規則，用來變相逼迫感染者走上被設定好的道路。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼......羅馬諾那傢伙從來不肯正視現實。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不阻止他的話，他真的有可能犯下不可饒恕的罪行。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#5$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g5_laboratory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，你看到的並不是怪物，也不是我的寵物。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們的確與我的實驗有關。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你承認了。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真相對你們而言並無益處。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道得越多，你們就越危險。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......替別人做決定，是不是你們這些上層人士最愛做的事？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先放下這些利器好不好？儀器都很脆弱。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者請瞄準這裡。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#4$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我不介意的。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她朝拓荒者們走了一步，弓弩幾乎碰到了她的身體。"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼的手微微顫抖了一下，他強迫自己將視線從那雙溫和的眼睛上移開。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是邪惡的伎倆，是迫使他們再次屈服的法術。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不怕死？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怕。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#2$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我更怕你們傷害自己。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，你不是兇手，你的同伴們也不是。你們只是一群想過上更好生活的普通人。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是也想過參加我的實驗嗎？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有機會的。只要加入我們，你就能得到你最渴望的東西。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我永遠不會對你們說不。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她向拓荒者們伸出了一隻手，彷彿正在等待他們握上去。"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她難道不明白，他們是來殺她的嗎？"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能看她。她的眼睛，她的手，全都不能看。太柔軟了。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從不得不走上荒野，城市和城市裡的人都在冷硬地說著拒絕。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她正在控制他們。她就是這樣控制住了那些可悲的意志軟弱的同伴。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是“機會”......"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個詞語，我們有多久沒聽見了？"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowshot", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_arrow_h"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#5$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "dialog", 